Schedule of Condition

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Condition

Note

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

General

Property exterior has been well maintained by landscape service. Property interior is in good condition

 

 

Condition

with signs of slight wear and tear noted in inventory. Cleaned to a professional standard. No major

 

 

problems noted at exterior or interior.

 

 

 

 

Decorative

The house has been professionally decorated with each room taking on a unique paint, wall paper, and

 

 

Condition

artwork combination.

 

 

 

 

 

Windows

Windows are all original single-hung with large shutters for privacy. All fully functional.

 

 

and

 

 

 

 

Treatment

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Flooring

Natural wood flooring with heavy use of decorative carpets. Kitchen and bathroom are tiled. Minor

 

 

 

wear and tear.

 

 

 

 

 

Lighting

Extensive use of decorative pendulum and wall sconce fixtures supplemented with recessed can

 

 

 

lighting creating a very well lit environment. Some accent lighting for artwork.

 

 

 

 

Kitchen

Modern stainless steel appliances and fixtures throughout. Gas stove/oven combination. Large granite

 

 

 

countertops and wood island. All fully functional.

 

 

 

 

Living

The entry, living room, dining, room, and bedroom are all in excellent condition and highly functional

 

 

Space

for intended use. There are a few minor items needing maintenance prior to occupancy.

 

 

 

 

Bathroom

Wood cabinets with dual sink integral counter. Modern well appointed fixtures. Tile floor with throw

 

 

 

rug.

Spaces

Entrance Hall

Notes: The Entrance Hall has a hardwood floor and the owner noted that the shelving with the figurines would be removed prior to rental.

The entrance hall is small and opens directly both onto the living room, and dining room. There is also a door to a half bathroom below the stairs.

ItemDescription

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Floors

 

 

Description: Wood

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

All of the floors are in similar condition and mostly covered by rugs in the Entrance hall, Living room, and Dining room.

The floors are hardwood and covered with a Persian rug. Both floor and rug are in good

condition.

Condition: Used

Walls & Paint

 

Description: Plaster Board

Walls are a taupe-brown color with white trim.

The walls are a tan color and appear to have some scuff marks and cracks due to age.

Condition: Worn

Needs Maintenance

Ceiling

 

Description: Plaster

The ceiling appears to have some damage that has been repaired. The finish surface is uneven, however the painted surface is in good condition.

Condition: New

There are doors to the laundry room, that are covered in a curtain. And a door into the dining room, that is a swinging door, that is white with brass fixtures.

Declaration

Whilst every care has been taken to ensure the accuracy of this schedule, accuracy cannot be guaranteed by the preparer.

The Landlord and the Tenant(s) are reminded that it is their responsibility to check the accuracy of this schedule and are advised to sign it in confirmation.

This inventory relates only to the furniture, furnishings and all Landlord's equipment and contents in the property. It is no guarantee of, or report on, the adequacy of, or safety of any such equipment or contents, merely a record that such items exist in the property at the date of the inventory and the superficial content of same.

This is to certify that we the undersigned have carefully checked the foregoing inventory and subject to the marginal notes, consider this to be a fair and correct schedule of condition of the contents therein.

The tenant/landlord has 7 days from receipt of this inventory to notify the agent/landlord/inventory company of any discrepancies.
